2 Ronde van Drenthe|49]]\n| [[2013 Ronde van Drenthe|11]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2014 Ronde van Drenthe|'''2''']]\n| [[2015 Ronde van Drenthe|22]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2016 Ronde van Drenthe|4]]\n| [[2017 Ronde van Drenthe|15]]\n| [[2018 Ronde van Drenthe|21]]\n| \u2014\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Omloop Het Nieuwsblad]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"| [[2013 Omloop Het Nieuwsblad (women's race)|8]]\n| [[2014 Omloop Het Nieuwsblad (women's race)|16]]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"| [[2015 Omloop Het Nieuwsblad (women's race)|'''1''']]\n| [[2016 Omloop Het Nieuwsblad (women's race)|14]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| [[2019 Omloop Het Nieuwsblad (women's race)|11]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Strade Bianche Donne]]\n| colspan=8 style=\"text-align:center; background:lightgrey;\"  colspan=6 {{N/a|Race did not exist}}\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   | [[2015 Strade Bianche Women|5]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   | [[2016 Strade Bianche Women|5]]\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:gold;\"| [[2018 Strade Bianche Women|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   | [[2019 Strade Bianche Women|9]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Trofeo Alfredo Binda]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|[[2012 Trofeo Alfredo Binda|21]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2013 Trofeo Alfredo Binda-Comune di Cittiglio|9]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2014 Trofeo Alfredo Binda-Comune di Cittiglio|4]]\n| style=\"background:#C9AE5D;\"|[[2015 Trofeo Alfredo Binda-Comune di Cittiglio|'''3''']]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2016 Trofeo Alfredo Binda-Comune di Cittiglio|6]]\n|[[2017 Trofeo Alfredo Binda-Comune di Cittiglio|DNF]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Gent\u2013Wevelgem]]\n| colspan=8 style=\"text-align:center; background:lightgrey;\"  colspan=3 {{N/a|Race did not exist}}\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| [[2016 Gent\u2013Wevelgem (women's race)|17]]\n| [[2017 Gent\u2013Wevelgem (women's race)|43]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Amstel Gold Race]]\n| colspan=8 {{N/a|Race did not exist}}\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2017 Amstel Gold Race (women's race)|'''1''']]\n|[[2018 Amstel Gold Race (women's race)|38]]\n|[[2019 Amstel Gold Race (women's race)|13]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne]]\n| [[2009 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|67]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| [[2012 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|12]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2013 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|4]]\n| [[2014 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|12]]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2015 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2016 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2017 La Fl\u00e8che Wallonne F\u00e9minine|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018 Fl\u00e8che Wallonne (women's race)|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2019 Fl\u00e8che Wallonne (women's race)|'''1''']]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[GP de Plouay]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| [[2011 GP de Plouay|60]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2012 GP de Plouay|4]]\n| style=\"background:#C9AE5D;\"|[[2013 GP de Plouay|'''3''']]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2014 GP de Plouay|5]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2015 GP de Plouay|6]]\n| \u2014\n| 19\n| \u2014\n|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:#efefef;\"|[[Open de Su\u00e8de V\u00e5rg\u00e5rda]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| [[2011 Open de Su\u00e8de V\u00e5rg\u00e5rda|62]]\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2013 Open de Su\u00e8de V\u00e5rg\u00e5rda|5]]\n| [[2014 Open de Su\u00e8de V\u00e5rg\u00e5rda|12]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"|[[2015 Open de Su\u00e8de V\u00e5rg\u00e5rda|5]]\n| \u2014\n| 19\n| 43\n|\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|colspan=16 align=center| '''Major championships timeline'''\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=2| Event\n! scope=\"col\" | 2010\n! scope=\"col\" | 2011\n! scope=\"col\" | 2012\n! scope=\"col\" | 2013\n! scope=\"col\" | 2014\n! scope=\"col\" | 2015\n! scope=\"col\" | 2016\n! scope=\"col\" | 2017\n! scope=\"col\" | 2018\n! scope=\"col\" | 2019\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2| [[File:Gold medal olympic.svg|15px|alt=|link=Gold medal]] [[List of Olympic medalists in cycling (women)|Olympic Games]]\n! scope=\"row\" | Time trial\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/a|Not held}}\n| \u2014\n| colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/a|Not held}}\n| style=\"background:#C9AE5D;\"|'''[[Cycling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's road time trial|3]]'''\n| colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/a|Not held}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" | Road race\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:gold;\"   | '''[[Cycling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's individual road race|1]]'''\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2| [[File:Jersey rainbow.svg|20px|alt=|link=Rainbow jersey]] [[UCI Road World Championships|World Championships]]\n! scope=\"row\"| [[UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|Time trial]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2015 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|'''2''']]\n| [[2016 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|13]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2017 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|'''2''']]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2018 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|'''2''']]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2019 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|'''2''']]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\"| [[UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|Road race]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   |[[2012 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|5]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   |[[2013 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|4]]\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2015 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|'''2''']]\n| [[2016 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|87]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   |[[2017 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|8]]\n| style=\"background:gold;\"   |[[2018 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|'''1''']]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\"|[[2019 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Women's road race|'''2''']]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2| [[File:EuropeanChampionJersey(2016).png|20px]] [[European Road Championships|European Championships]]\n! scope=\"row\"| Time trial\n| colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/a|Event did not exist}}\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\" |[[2016 European Road Championships \u2013 Women's time trial|'''2''']]\n| style=\"background:#C9AE5D;\" |[[2017 European Road Championships|'''3''']]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0;\" |[[2018 European Road Cycling Championships|'''2''']]\n| \u2014\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"row\"| Road race\n| style=\"background:gold;\"   |[[2016 European Road Championships|'''1''']]\n| [[2017 European Road Championships|70]]\n| style=\"background:#ddf;\"   |[[2018 European Road Cycling Championships|8]]\n| \u2014\n|}\n\n:\u2013 = Did not start\n:DNF = Did not finish\n\n==See also==\n* [[UCI Women's Road World Cup]]\n* [[UCI Women's World Tour]]\n* [[List of women's road bicycle races]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{cycling archives|34070}}\n*{{ProCyclingStats|139268}