eason (programming language)|Reason]]\n* [[REBOL]]\n* [[Red (programming language)|Red]]\n* [[Core War|Redcode]]\n<!-- REALbasic is on the BASIC dialects list - see [[List of BASIC dialects]] page -->\n* [[REFAL]]\n* [[REXX]]\n* [http://rittle.org Rittle]\n* [[Rlab]]\n* [[ROOP (programming language)|ROOP]]\n* [[IBM RPG|RPG]]\n* [[RPL (programming language)|RPL]]\n* [[Robot Battle#Robot scripting language|RSL]]\n* [[RTL/2]]\n* [[Ruby (programming language)|Ruby]]\n<!-- Ruby on Rails is a Ruby library, not a programming language -->\n* [[Rust (programming language)|Rust]]\n}}\n\n== S ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em|\n* [[S (programming language)|S]]\n* [[S2 (programming language)|S2]]\n* [[S3 (programming language)|S3]]\n* [[S-Lang (programming language)|S-Lang]]\n* [[S-PLUS]]\n* [[SA-C (programming language)|SA-C]]\n* [[SabreTalk]]\n* [[SAIL (programming language)|SAIL]]\n* [[SAM76]]\n* [[SAS System|SAS]]\n* [[SASL (programming language)|SASL]]\n* [[Sather]]\n* [[Sawzall (programming language)|Sawzall]]\n* [[Scala (programming language)|Scala]]\n* [[Scheme (programming language)|Scheme]]\n* [[Scilab]]\n* [[Scratch (programming language)|Scratch]]\n* [[Script.NET]]\n* [[Sed]]\n* [[Seed7]]\n* [[Self (programming language)|Self]]\n* [[SenseTalk]]\n* [[SequenceL]]\n* [[Ethereum#Programming languages|Serpent]]\n* [[SETL]]\n* [[Superbase database#History|SIMPOL]]\n<!-- Shake Speare belongs on the esoteric page -->\n* [[SIGNAL (programming language)|SIGNAL]]\n* [[SiMPLE]]\n* [[SIMSCRIPT]]\n* [[Simula]]\n* [[Simulink]]\n* [[Singularity (operating system)|Singularity]]\n* [[SISAL]]\n* [[SLIP (programming language)|SLIP]]\n* [[SMALL]]\n<!-- [[Small Basic]] \u2013 see [[List of BASIC dialects]] -->\n* [[Smalltalk]]\n<!-- [[Microsoft Small Basic|Small Basic]] - see [[List of BASIC dialects]] page -->\n* [[Standard ML|SML]]\n* [[Strongtalk]]\n* [[Snap! (programming language)|Snap!]]\n* [[SNOBOL]] ([[SPITBOL compiler|SPITBOL]])\n* [[Snowball programming language|Snowball]]\n* [[S